mutual
  Γ⊢τ-thinning-size : (Γ⊂Γ' : k by Γ ⊂' Γ')
                    → (Γ'ok : Γ' ok)
                    → (δ : Γ ⊢ τ)
                    → size-twf (Γ⊢τ-thinning Γ⊂Γ' Γ'ok δ)
                      ≤
                      size-twf δ + size-ok Γ'ok
