Γ⊢τ-weakening-size : (Γok : Γ ok)
                   → (Γ⊢τ' : Γ ⊢ τ')
                   → (Γ⊢τ : Γ ⊢ τ)
                   → size-twf (Γ⊢τ-weakening Γok Γ⊢τ' Γ⊢τ)
                     ≤
                     size-twf Γ⊢τ + suc (size-ok Γok ⊕ size-twf Γ⊢τ')
Γ⊢τ-weakening-size Γok Γ⊢τ' Γ⊢τ = Γ⊢τ-thinning-size ignore-head (TCTX-Bind Γok Γ⊢τ') Γ⊢τ
